My recommendations for Windows
Install Windows Terminal from the Microsoft Store (much better than Command Prompt).
Use PowerShell or Windows Terminal instead of Command Prompt.
Install Git for Windows.
Install VS Code with these extensions later:
Python
Flutter
Dart
GitLens (optional)
Your PC should ideally have
Windows 10 or Windows 11 ✅
8 GB RAM minimum (16 GB is even better)
At least 50 GB free disk space
An Intel or AMD processor with virtualization enabled (helps with the Android emulator)
